                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm hover-effect">
                <img src="~/Image/index03.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="多種新鮮的水果和蔬菜" style="height: 400px; object-fit: cover;">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">農產品簡介</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">我們的農場提供多種新鮮的水果和茶葉，讓您享受自然的美味。果茶庄園以其豐富多樣的農產品而聞名，提供新鮮美味的水果和優質的茶葉。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm hover-effect">
                <img src="~/Image/index02.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="有趣的活動，如摘水果和農場遊覽" style="height: 400px; object-fit: cover;">
                <div class="card-body">
